It would be great to have something similar to JIRA's transitions for basic page operations.

JIRA's trasitions can define conditions, validators and post-functions. The idea is to have something similar for creating and editing pages. For example, the trigger could force a change comment to be included, or a variable to be defined. It may check that the page is not empty or that the title is not duplicated.

Also, you could automatically restrict page editing so that further changes need to be previously approved by page or space admin.

